st order structural transformation to a high pressure phase around\n5-6 GPa. From the predicted detonation properties, ADN is found to have high\nand low performance characteristics when compared with ammonium based energetic\noxidizers and well-known secondary explosives, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Sep 2016 05:39:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-05"}
