1.22\\sqrt{ J}, 0.16/\\sqrt{\nJ})$ where $\\Omega$ is the angular velocity of KBH. Furthermore we draw the\nphase diagrams in both $(M, J)$ and $(M,\\Omega)$ coordinates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Sep 2016 15:01:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2016 16:15:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-08"}
